eventDecorators.name: Transfer
eventDecorators.description: Validator's status changed. Event emitted for each executed trade.

functionDecorators.name: resolver
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address of the resolver for the specified node.

functionDecorators.name: owner
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address that owns the specified node.

functionDecorators.name: setSubnodeOwner
functionDecorators.description: Transfers ownership of a subnode keccak256(node, label) to a new address. May only be called by the owner of the parent node.

parameterDecorators.name: label
parameterDecorators.description: The hash of the label specifying the subnode.

parameterDecorators.name: owner
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the new owner.

functionDecorators.name: setTTL
functionDecorators.description: Sets the TTL for the specified node.

functionDecorators.name: ttl
functionDecorators.description: Returns the TTL of a node, and any records associated with it.

functionDecorators.name: setResolver
functionDecorators.description: Sets the resolver address for the specified node.

functionDecorators.name: setOwner
functionDecorators.description: Transfers ownership of a node to a new address. May only be called by the current owner of the node.

parameterDecorators.name: node
parameterDecorators.description: The node to transfer ownership of.

parameterDecorators.name: owner
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the new owner.
